name: JSONGenerator
description: Contains methods used to serialize objects into JSON content using the standard JSON encoding.

isclosed().name: isClosed
isclosed().description: Returns true if the JSON generator is closed; otherwise, returns false.

writeblob(blob).name: writeBlob
writeblob(blob).description: Writes the specified Blob value as a base64-encoded string.

writeblobfield(string,blob).name: writeBlobField
writeblobfield(string,blob).signature: public void writeBlobField(String fieldName, Blob blobValue)
writeblobfield(string,blob).description: Writes a field name and value pair using the specified field name and BLOB value.

writebooleanfield(string,boolean).name: writeBooleanField
writebooleanfield(string,boolean).signature: public void writeBooleanField(String fieldName, Boolean booleanValue)
writebooleanfield(string,boolean).description: Writes a field name and value pair using the specified field name and Boolean value.

writedate(date).name: writeDate
writedate(date).description: Writes the specified date value in the ISO-8601 format.

writedatefield(string,date).name: writeDateField
writedatefield(string,date).signature: public void writeDateField(String fieldName, Date dateValue)
writedatefield(string,date).description: Writes a field name and value pair using the specified field name and date value. The date value is written in the ISO-8601 format.

writedatetime(datetime).name: writeDateTime
writedatetime(datetime).description: Writes the specified date and time value in the ISO-8601 format.

writedatetimefield(string,datetime).name: writeDateTimeField
writedatetimefield(string,datetime).signature: public void writeDateTimeField(String fieldName, Datetime datetimeValue)
writedatetimefield(string,datetime).description: Writes a field name and value pair using the specified field name and date and time value. The date and time value is written in the ISO-8601 format.

writeendarray().name: writeEndArray
writeendarray().description: Writes the ending marker of a JSON array (']').

writeendobject().name: writeEndObject
writeendobject().description: Writes the ending marker of a JSON object ('}').

writeidfield(string,id).name: writeIdField
writeidfield(string,id).signature: public void writeIdField(String fieldName, Id identifier)
writeidfield(string,id).description: Writes a field name and value pair using the specified field name and identifier value.

writenull().name: writeNull
writenull().description: Writes the JSON null literal value.

writenullfield(string).name: writeNullField
writenullfield(string).description: Writes a field name and value pair using the specified field name and the JSON null literal value.

writenumberfield(string,decimal).name: writeNumberField
writenumberfield(string,decimal).signature: public void writeNumberField(String fieldName, Decimal number)
writenumberfield(string,decimal).description: Writes a field name and value pair using the specified field name and decimal value.

writenumberfield(string,double).name: writeNumberField
writenumberfield(string,double).signature: public void writeNumberField(String fieldName, Double number)
writenumberfield(string,double).description: Writes a field name and value pair using the specified field name and double value.

writenumberfield(string,integer).name: writeNumberField
writenumberfield(string,integer).signature: public void writeNumberField(String fieldName, Integer number)
writenumberfield(string,integer).description: Writes a field name and value pair using the specified field name and integer value.

writenumberfield(string,long).name: writeNumberField
writenumberfield(string,long).signature: public void writeNumberField(String fieldName, Long number)
writenumberfield(string,long).description: Writes a field name and value pair using the specified field name and long value.

writeobject(object).name: writeObject
writeobject(object).description: Writes the specified Apex object in JSON format.

writeobjectfield(string,object).name: writeObjectField
writeobjectfield(string,object).signature: public void writeObjectField(String fieldName, Object value)
writeobjectfield(string,object).description: Writes a field name and value pair using the specified field name and Apex object.

writestartarray().name: writeStartArray
writestartarray().description: Writes the starting marker of a JSON array ('[').

writestartobject().name: writeStartObject
writestartobject().description: Writes the starting marker of a JSON object ('{').

writestringfield(string,string).name: writeStringField
writestringfield(string,string).signature: public void writeStringField(String fieldName, String stringValue)
writestringfield(string,string).description: Writes a field name and value pair using the specified field name and string value.

writetime(time).name: writeTime
writetime(time).description: Writes the specified time value in the ISO-8601 format.

writetimefield(string,time).name: writeTimeField
writetimefield(string,time).signature: public void writeTimeField(String fieldName, Time timeValue)
writetimefield(string,time).description: Writes a field name and value pair using the specified field name and time value in the ISO-8601 format.
